These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: gardening, fishing, woodworking, rock-climbing, magic-tricks, filmmaking
6 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, hedgehog, mouse, rabbit
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not the owner of the mouse##6
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 5. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 7. the owner of the mouse is not the person who's hobby is fishing##6
 8. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
11. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
12. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
13. the owner of the cat is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
14. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
15. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing   | gardening | woodworking   | filmmaking     | fishing    | magic-tricks   |
| Pet           | mouse | cat   | rabbit | hedgehog | guinea-pig | goldfish |

