.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: disaster, documentary, drama, fantasy, horror, time-travel
House: art-deco, futuristic, tower, townhouse, cape-cod, craftsman
 1. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching documentary movies##5
 2. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 3. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
 4. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
 6. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 7. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
 8. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching horror movies is not the cape-cod house##6
10. the art-deco house is somewhere between the craftsman house and the townhouse house##7
11. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the person watching horror movies##5
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the futuristic house##1
13. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
14. the craftsman house is in an even position##4
15. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the townhouse house##5
16. the craftsman house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
17. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the futuristic house and the person watching horror movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | time-travel | fantasy | horror     | drama      | disaster |
| House           | futuristic         | tower        | cape-cod   | townhouse | art-deco | craftsman    |

