 3. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is not the owner of the rabbit##6
 6. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the owner of the rabbit##7
 7. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the horse##7
 8. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 9. the person watching crime movies is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the owner of the mouse##7
10. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
12. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
13. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the mouse##1
14. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
