 6. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
 8. the fan of punk is somewhere between the fan of gospel and the fan of blues##7
 9. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
10. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking juice is the fan of classical##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is not the fan of classical##6
