 4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5
 6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person driving the boat##2
 7. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person driving the trike##5
11. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
12. the person driving the tram is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the person driving the motorbike##7
13. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Sport         | rugby   | tennis | skateboarding      | cricket | soccer  | handball   |
| Transport   | train | trike  | motorbike | boat   | tram | skateboard |

