.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: june, october, july, december, november, february
The people have 6 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, fisherman, journalist, project-manager, scientist
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the fisherman##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the journalist and the dressmaker##7
 5. the scientist is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is the project-manager##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
 8. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 9. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
10. the dressmaker is somewhere to the right of the scientist##5
11. the scientist is on the right of the fisherman##1
12. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the journalist##5
13. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in july##7
14. the dressmaker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
15. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Birthday   | july         | december | october | june   | february | november  |
| Job     | project-manager | journalist  | fisherman  | scientist | dressmaker  | accountant |

 